      "side": 1,
      "message": "uber-nit: might be nice to merge CountFooQuery and CountFooRows so that we only need to lock c.countersMtx once instead of twice.\n\nI think this would simplify most call sites, e.g.\n  c.CountReadQuery(ref.Path)\n  c.CountReadRows(ref.Path, 1)\nbecomes\n  c.CountReadQuery(ref.Path, 1)\n\nalthough others are a little more complicated, e.g.\n  c.CountReadQuery(ref.Path)\n  it :\u003d ref.Collections(ctx)\n  for {\n    ...\n    c.CountReadRows(ref.Path, 1)\n  }\nbecomes\n  count :\u003d 0\n  it :\u003d ref.Collections(ctx)\n  for {\n    ...\n    count++\n  }\n  c.CountReadQuery(ref.Path, count)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 219,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 223,
        "endChar": 0
      },
